{
  "stem": "10397.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We pay five times as much because that's for the-- and-- Ministry of Internal Affairs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the Department of Building Strategic Highways had nothing to do with secret service.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they gave me a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was the head of the-- head doctor for those 5,000-- the prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In five points, I got a pair of horses, and a-- and a-- and a car, and special restaurant to eat, and a secretary, and I had a big shot, and paid me.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had-- and there was such a supply house-- supply store where they gave me certain materials to make a pair of pants, and buy groceries, and buy toiletries.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so forth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my-- my secretary was not allowed to go where I go, because she was only a secretary-- a-- a smaller portion of material for a skirt, a different restaurant-- that's the-- the Communist, you know, equality.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's-- and then-- and then I got the job for my father there-- head of the warehouse of instrument-- tools-- tools.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because-- and they-- the officers-- the prisoners were treated very well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Once a week, they went to bath-- to the-- to take baths, and delousing machine-- delousing such containers, and food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And no-- no physical abuse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they had to go to work every week-- every day in the morning, 6 o'clock, under guard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There's guards.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They had to go to the-- to the-- road and work for eight hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But they had-- they got a cold lunch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they got a-- a hot dinner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when you needed laundry or something-- when your shirt got torn to be thrown away, they gave you a shirt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They gave you underwear until the-- till 1941 when the Germans invaded Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
